For PayPal’s purposes, carry out the transaction as if you were selling the other person your goods.2) Each of you must pay the received money request. PayPal will ultimately deduct 88 cents from each of you for the transaction. 3) Send each other the items in the agreed upon fashion. If you are both sending it through mail, make sure you send it with some kind of shipping tracking number. 4) Enjoy your traded item, and send a quick thank you message to your trading partner so he knows you received the goodsNote: In your money request, include a note outlining the details of the sale.
